		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><span class="name"><a name="284619"></a><b>Kapaal</b></span><br /><span class="postdetails">Elementalist<br /><br /><br />Joined: 27 Aug 2003<br />Posts: 129<br /></span><br /></td>
